## Requirements

[Install Powerline](https://powerline.readthedocs.org/en/latest/overview.html#installation):

    $ pip install --user git+git://github.com/Lokaltog/powerline

Add Powerline directory to your local Vim configuration:

    " ~/.vimrcl
    set rtp+=~/.local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/powerline/bindings/vim

## Installation

    $ bash < <(curl -s https://raw.github.com/tobiassjosten/dotfiles/master/install)

Install Vim bundles:

    $ vim +BundleInstall +qall
